===Noun===
'''tetragon''' (''plural'' '''tetragons''')

#(''geometry; rare'') A [[quadrilateral]].

====Note====

Although consistent with [[pentagon]], [[hexagon]], etc., this term is not the common one; '''quadrilateral''' is the more common term.

